thread.title: ‘Pacific Rim Uprising’ Dethrones ‘Black Panther’

author: wsjcom
title: ‘Pacific Rim Uprising’ Dethrones ‘Black Panther’
text:
NEW YORK—It took six weeks but “Black Panther” has finally been unseated as the top film at the North American box office.
The monsters-versus-robots science-fiction sequel “Pacific Rim Uprising” dethroned the superhero sensation with $28 million in ticket sales, according to studio estimates Sunday.
